fields.description: The Champion Rhino Stretch Training Fitness Bands are great for muscle, strength and flexibility training. These versatile resistance bands are also a great option for group fitness classes that focus on cardio and maintenance. These multi-use fitness bands also promote safe stretching, proper form and can be useful when rehabilitating injuries. The Rhino training bands are offered in resistance levels from 5lbs to 100lbs. Resistance band exercises are easy with the lighter resistance level bands and gradually get tougher all the way up to the super heavy resistance level. These bands are an essential part of any fitness class or personal workout routine.

fields.name: KETTLEBELLS
fields.description: Kettlebells are one of the simplest and yet most broadly functional pieces of fitness equipment. You get the same full-body strength work as a conventional movements without worrying about scraped shins and maintaining leg contact with the barbell. The Hex Trap bar improves lifting efficiency and relieves lower back stress by lifting with arms by your sides in a neutral grip instead of in front of your body.
